headline: Spotting Winners: Fortive (NYSE:FTV) And Professional Tools and Equipment Stocks In Q1
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how professional tools and equipment stocks fared in Q1, starting with Fortive (NYSE:FTV).
